videos.description: QB Dwayne Haskins sends a long pass downfield to Terry McLaurin for Ohio State's first touchdown of the game.
videos.headline: Haskins finds McLaurin on 41-yd TD

videos.description: The Golden Gophers answer the Buckeyes' touchdown with another rushing score in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Minnesota scores again on Ohio State

videos.description: Coney Durr is ejected after he was called for targeting on Ohio State QB Dwayne Haskins.
videos.headline: Minnesota's Durr ejected for targeting

videos.description: Urban Meyer reacts after Minnesota's defense stops Ohio State from converting on 4th down in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Ohio State stuffed on 4th down

videos.description: Shaun Wade forces Tyler Johnson to fumble, setting the Buckeyes up with great field position.
videos.headline: Ohio State recovers Minnesota's fumble

videos.description: K.J. Hill hauls in Dwayne Haskins' 36-yard pass with one hand, giving Ohio State the lead over Minnesota.
videos.headline: Hill's 1-handed grab leads to Ohio State TD
